citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 12:50 on
27-Feb-19.
Arrived at premises at 12:50. Knocked on door, called both contact numbers and left messages at both. Waited 30
minutes with no response. Departed at 13:30.
